snippet.title: 달의 전설[月の伝説](Legend of The Moon)
snippet.description:
[Download]https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GoZipGame.LOMFREE

For those who get sick and tired of endless and meaningless levelup 
we developed it so they can get nostalgic about the moment you held a controller to see the ending part when young.
